reviews.text: Jade has been a joy to work with - knowledgeable, reliable and great at tuning into what I wanted to achieve in my new home. I reached out to her to reduce overwhelm and her in-person power sessions were great! She helped me channel my thinking and make decisions -  so no more going round in circles. I wholeheartedly recommend Jade and I will definitely reach out to her again in the future. Thank you Jade for all your help!

I was looking for some help to tie together the colour scheme, layout and design elements of my newly built open plan kitchen / living space and came to Jade for some help via her Power Hour session. She came to my house and helped me nail down the colour scheme and bounce some ideas I had as well as giving me so many tips and helpful direction when it comes to styling the space. I was really impressed with the follow up after and the resources she put together. I would highly recommend jade, she was efficient, prepared, creative, helpful and honestly has helped me so much to ensure that the space felt put together and cosy!

Jade transformed our tricky, dark, under-the-roof shower room into a beautiful, light and airy family bathroom that feels like a hotel! I had a few ideas of what I wanted but Jade really knew how to pull it all together into a modern design that also fits with the rest of the house decor. I knew her design would be beautiful as I had already seen pictures of her previous work, and we were blown away by the 3D computer rendering, which really helped us to imagine the space. Once completed, it was even better than I imagined! Somehow she managed to add a bathtub to our existing setup and yet the whole space feels even larger than before - the hallmark of a great designer! She was also able to advise and adapt when our builders needed a workaround, so that we were able to keep the design as true to the original as possible. We wouldn't hesitate to recommend Jade: she's professional, problem-solving, practically minded and a very talented designer. We hope to work with her again on future projects.

I am really happy with the design that Jade did for my bedroom. She listened to what we wanted and came up with initial concepts that were then revised based on our feedback before producing the final design,

Jade was excellent! She listened to our ideas and got a good feel of our house and the needs we had.
Her designs are easy to understand and gave us a great picture of what our room would look like.
I highly recommend her !

name: MS Decorating
address: Rogate Road, Hill Brow, Liss GU33 7QP, UK

reviews.text: Fabulous quality of workmanship, extremely reliable, friendly and trustworthy. I can highly recommend MS Decorating. They did a lot of remedial work on our new build and got it up to a much higher standard which we were delighted with.

Fantastic service from start to finish! Max was knowledgeable about the products, polite, punctual and very trustworthy. The job was completed quickly and to a really high standard, leaving everything neat and tidy. We’re so pleased with the results and wouldn’t hesitate to use him again. Highly recommend!

"The Boys" as we affectionally knew them did another fantastic job. This is their second visit in a couple of months and the standards they set are of the very highest order. They are very neat and tidy and very polite and helpful. This time we tested both painting and wallpapering skills and another 10/10. I see that they are spraying the paint on now and it gives the paint a lovely even and solid look. Their work is so clean from masking up to the final piece of rubbish being removed. I cannot praise them enough and would recommend without reservation. They will shortly be returning to do our bedrooms and en-suites.

Absolutely delighted with the experience of having such a professional interaction and a professional job. Going above and beyond to get the bathroom done in a timely tidy clean and in an unobtrusive way. Look forward to the next phase of decoration and having your input in colour and design again- couldn’t recommend MS Decorating more highly.
Max was great and redecorated whole house, communication was good and always clean and tidy at end of each day.. would highly recommend

name: Lee Baker Professional Decorating Services
address: 6 Astrid Cl, Hayling Island PO11 9PR, UK

reviews.text: Lee Baker's Decorating really is top notch. They totally transformed our home with their UPVC spraying, making it look fresh. If you want your place reinvigorated, Lee Baker's Decorating is the way to go. Super friendly, super talented – can't recommend them enough! Lee and his team always ensured our home was well looked after while they worked and left it absolutely spotless once they had finished. Thank you so much..

Lee Baker Decorating has been a godsend for our Victorian house! Their expertise in restoring key features has been invaluable in bringing out the beauty of our home's heritage. From intricate moldings to original woodwork, they've worked wonders in preserving and enhancing the charm of our Victorian-era home. We couldn't be happier with the results. If you have a historic home in need of some TLC, Lee Baker Decorating is the team to trust!

Lee Baker professional Decorating did an incredible job transforming our home! From painting every room to spraying our doors and kitchen, their work exceeded our expectations. The UPVC spraying was a game-changer! Professional, reliable, and meticulous attention to detail. Highly recommend Lee Baker for any painting and decorating needs!

Lee has done a fabulous job on restoring my seafront home to its full potential. You cannot fault his workmanship and the advice given. Lee is extremely professional, trustworthy and efficient. It was  a pleasure to do business with Lee. Thank you

Lee's team do an excellent job, very professional, clean and tidy providing a great finish to walls and ceiling making them look as new as the first time they were painted. Polite and friendly, I would recommend them to anyone who is looking for a great finish for a great price.

name: Brewer C A, Painter and Decorator

reviews.text:
C A Brewer Painter & Decorator made a fantastic job of painting the interior of our house. Walls, Ceilings and Woodwork, upstairs and down.
He arrived bright & early each morning and immediately set to work, barely stopping for a break. Courteous and diligent, and extremely professional, I could not have wanted for a better Tradesman.
There was no mess, everything was diligently covered and the finish was top class. I would highly recommend Colin to anybody looking to redecorate their home.

Colin recently decorated by extension, living room and stairway and I am extremely pleased with the results!
Extremely professional, diligent, works swiftly and cleanly and very reasonable! I would recommend him to anyone who is looking for decorating and painting services.  I shall certainly be asking Colin back to do more work for me.
Colin turned up at the agreed time to start the work at our house , he is very professional, reliable and extremely trustworthy. His work was excellent and we will definitely use his services again .

I have used C A Brewer painter and decorator many times over the years to decorate properties that I let. They are very professional and do a great job at a fair price. Would definitely use again and would definitely recommend.

From decorating to landscaping, large to small, Charlie has done numerous jobs at my house.  These include:
Laying carpet tiles
Total interior decorations, both paint and paper
Decking repairs
Patio laying
Exterior painting
Always completed to a very high standard, and with a smile.  Charlie is highly recommended.

Charlie carried out three jobs for us - installation of a decking area; laying a path; and fixing trellis panels to a boundary fence. All three fully met our requirements and were carried out to a high standard. We would not hesitate to recommend him.
Charlie replaced our ageing wood panelling above our porch. Great job, would recommend 100%
